{"id":15524,"date":"2024-08-30T16:44:30","date_gmt":"2024-08-30T09:44:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=15524"},"modified":"2024-08-30T16:44:30","modified_gmt":"2024-08-30T09:44:30","slug":"phi-truoc-ba-oto-lap-rap-trong-nuoc-duoc-giam-3-thang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/phi-truoc-ba-oto-lap-rap-trong-nuoc-duoc-giam-3-thang\/","title":{"rendered":"Ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 \u00f4t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m 3 th\u00e1ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"description\">\u00d4t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 r\u01a1 mo\u00f3c ho\u1eb7c s\u01a1 mi r\u01a1 mo\u00f3c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m 50% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 trong 3 th\u00e1ng, t\u1eeb 1\/9.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Theo Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 ban h\u00e0nh h\u00f4m 29\/8, l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 n\u1ed9p l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u00f4t\u00f4, r\u01a1 mo\u00f3c ho\u1eb7c s\u01a1mi r\u01a1 mo\u00f3c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i xe t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m 50%, t\u1eeb 1\/9 \u0111\u1ebfn 30\/11. T\u1eeb 1\/12, l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed n\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c c\u0169.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp xe s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y r\u00fat ng\u1eafn m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y (6 th\u00e1ng). Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, gi\u1ea3m ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 xe nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 xe l\u0103n b\u00e1nh. Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m lo\u1ea1i ph\u00ed n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u1eb1m k\u00edch c\u1ea7u ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng xe trong n\u01b0\u1edbc trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Theo s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VAMA), n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, t\u1ed5ng doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n \u00f4t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p, s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t trong n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t 67.849 xe, gi\u1ea3m 15% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. T\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 4, doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n \u00f4t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p, s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t trong n\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n xe nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u nguy\u00ean chi\u1ebfc 3-14%.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/phi-truoc-ba-oto-lap-rap-trong-nuoc-duoc-giam-3-thang\/oto-lap-rap-trong-nuoc-jpeg-71-4809-1736-1722424568\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-15525\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15525\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/oto-lap-rap-trong-nuoc-jpeg-71-4809-1736-1722424568.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/oto-lap-rap-trong-nuoc-jpeg-71-4809-1736-1722424568.jpg 680w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/oto-lap-rap-trong-nuoc-jpeg-71-4809-1736-1722424568-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/oto-lap-rap-trong-nuoc-jpeg-71-4809-1736-1722424568-480x320.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Hi\u1ec7n l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 xe con \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khi \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u00f4t\u00f4 con t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0 12% gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb xe; TP HCM 10%, H\u00e0 T\u0129nh 11%&#8230; Ri\u00eang xe b\u00e1n t\u1ea3i, ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 b\u1eb1ng 60% m\u1ee9c thu ph\u00ed l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi xe con. T\u1eeb l\u1ea7n n\u1ed9p l\u1ec7 th\u1ee9 hai, m\u1ee9c thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 l\u00e0 2% v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, khi x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, B\u1ed9 T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian qua Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch khi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng gi\u1eefa xe s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u. \u0110\u1ec3 \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3, B\u1ed9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 giao B\u1ed9 C\u00f4ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u00e0 so\u00e1t, \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n x\u1eed l\u00fd trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u01af\u1edbc t\u00ednh, ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m thu kho\u1ea3ng 2.600 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"tplCaption action_thumb_added\" data-size=\"true\"><figcaption><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00d4t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 r\u01a1 mo\u00f3c ho\u1eb7c s\u01a1 mi r\u01a1 mo\u00f3c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m 50% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 trong 3 th\u00e1ng, t\u1eeb 1\/9. Theo Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 ban h\u00e0nh h\u00f4m 29\/8, l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 n\u1ed9p l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u00f4t\u00f4, r\u01a1 mo\u00f3c ho\u1eb7c s\u01a1mi r\u01a1 mo\u00f3c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15525,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15524"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15524"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15524\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":15527,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15524\/revisions\/15527"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15525"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15524"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15524"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15524"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=15524"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}